    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, quick question. im taking sertraline (50mg) for my mood but i feel like it's not quite doing enough for me lately since finals are coming up. i was thinking about adding some st. john's wort to my routine to help boost things naturally. is it okay to take those together or is there any reason i shouldn't?",
