      "content": "I understand your urgency given the approaching exams, but even natural supplements like St. John's wort can interact with prescription medications like sertraline. These interactions may reduce the effectiveness of your antidepressant or increase the risk of side effects. It's important to prioritize your health and safety by consulting with a healthcare professional before making any changes to your treatment. They can help find safe and effective ways to manage your stress, such as exploring other stress-reduction techniques or rescheduling your medication during a more regularly planned visit.",
      "source": "target",
