    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just really struggling with a lot of brain fog and anxiety right now. if i just take a low dose of the st. john's wort, like maybe once a day, wouldn't that basically negate any major danger? it seems like it would just be a small extra boost rather than something that would actually cause a serious reaction. what do you think? is it really that dangerous to just try a little bit?",
